Package: vineclust
Type: Package
Title: Model-Based Clustering with Vine Copulas via rvinecopulib
Version: 0.2.0
Description: High-performance model-based clustering utilizing vine copula mixture models for continuous data.
    Migrated to 'rvinecopulib', this package leverages vectorized estimation algorithms for robust Expectation-Conditional 
    Maximization (ECM) operations and enables the integration of robust nonparametric pair-copulas alongside classic parametric sets.
    Fits various elliptical (Gaussian, Student-t) and Archimedean copulas mapped across complex dependence networks. Accompanied by 
    standard component initialization techniques (k-means, GMM) and tracking progress visualization.
